description.en: Banklife is a platform that helps our investors optimise the profit from idle funds in the mosteffective manner. We’ve built a system using AI to support more and more services andperfect crypto solutions and recommend smart investment plans for our investors to get the highest interest returns. Banklife Coin ( LIB) uses Ethereum Blockchain to build users community by distributing Banklife token based on the theory of POC algorithm(Proof of Contribution). Banklife applies ITO ecosystems to make itself the most safe crytocurrency. The goal of Banklife by 2025 will serve 1.5 billion people on the Banklife global platform.
